# billpocket-java-challenge

https://www.billpocket.com:8443/cpmx2017/javaChallenge

Java/Kotlin Challenge

At Billpocket's HQ, we devs love movies and cryptography. Our favorite game is "Guess the movie from the crypto-quote", where we encrypt movie quotes so others can try and guess the movie by decrypting them.

At Campus Party 2017, we want everyone to have a great time with us and we've selected 4 of these quotes to play with you. As a rookie in this extreme sport, we've chosen to give you a head start and included hints on every quote which will help you decoding the next one.

To be sure you're not cheating, you must provide proof-of-work by showing the neatly documented, high-performant Java/Kotlin code your brain executed to unveil these mysteries.

Feeling 1337 h4x0r today? We'll let you know how to send your answers when you uncover the last quote.
